            <h2>Lot Polish Airlines Refund Policy</h2>

            <p>Lot Airlines is a major airline in Poland that serves both domestic and international flights. Lot Airlines provide flexibility and benefits to a large extent for the passengers while booking their flights. </p>

            <h2>Cancellation Policy</h2>

            <p>According to Lot Polish Airlines ' hour <a href="https://www.faresmatch.com/lot-polish-airlines-cancellation-policy.aspx">cancellation policy</a>, passengers can cancel their scheduled flights on Lot Polish Airlines within 24 hours of purchasing tickets. If any passenger cancels their flight within 24 hours, Lot Airlines won't charge any penalty regardless of the fare selected. </p>

            <p>If a passenger has purchased a basic economy <a href="https://www.faresmatch.com/lot-polish-airlines.aspx">Lot Polish Airline ticket</a>, they are not permitted to cancel the ticket for a refund after 24 hours. A non-refundable Airline ticket requires a fare difference. If the <a href="https://www.faresmatch.com/">Airline ticket</a> is refundable, then the passenger can cancel the ticket any time before the flight's departure. The passenger would be reimbursed on their original method of payment. </p>

            <h3>Refund Policy</h3>

            <p>The passenger can <a href="https://www.faresmatch.com/lot-polish-airlines-refund-policy.aspx">file a refund request form online at Lot Polish Airlines' </a>official website to get a refund. The refund is only provided on eligible Lot Polish Airline <a href="https://www.faresmatch.com/">flight tickets</a> that are cancelled within the given period, 24 hours. The refund request of Lot Polish Airlines may take14 days to process the refund. </p>

            <p>The airline doesn't provide refunds if the period has expired. If the ticket is cancelled after 24 hours, the refund will be compensated for future travel credit. If the flight is cancelled due to unavoidable circumstances from the airline's end, it provides the passenger with compensation to book the next flight. </p>

            <h2>FAQs</h2>

            <h3>Can I cancel the Lot Polish Airlines flight within 24 hours’ time period? </h3>
            <p>Yes, you can cancel the flight without paying any penalty within 24 hours. If the time exceeds 24 hours, then some fare difference must be paid to the airline. </p>
            <h3>What happens if a passenger cancels a non-refundable flight? </h3>
            <p>In the case of non-refundable flights, the passenger needs to pay a fare difference. The fare amount depends on the length of the flight, destination and the type of fare. The rest of the fare is given to the passenger as credit for future travel on Lot Polish Airlines. </p>
            <h3>How can we cancel a flight on Lot Polish Airlines? </h3>
            <p>You can cancel the flight online through your mobile devices or laptops. You can also cancel the flight by calling Lot Polish Airlines Department. Another option is to cancel the ticket at the airport. For this, you need to go to Lot Polish Airlines ATO (Airport Ticket Office) </p>
            <h3>Does the Lot contact centre work 24 hours for the cancellation of flights? </h3>
            <p>Yes, the Lot contact centre works 24/7 to help the passengers to cancel their flights. Therefore, you can easily cancel your flights with the help of professionals by approaching the contact centre. </p>
            <h3>How to get back the flight voucher when the airline cancels its flight? </h3>
            <p>In case of cancellation of a flight, the Airlines give vouchers valid for future travel. By visiting the official website of Lot Airlines, you can redeem it. </p>
